OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778796671
OL,3,CPolitical chaos is bad for the economy
OL,4,Cno matter who is in charge
OL,6,FDespite the political uncertainty,
OL,7,Fthere was good news on economic growth
OL,8,Fon Thursday, but challenges remain,
OL,9,FITV News Economic Editor Joel Hills
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FDaybreak, Thursday 14 May. GDP day.
OL,13,FAnd as the Office for National
OL,14,FStatistics published its latest update
OL,15,Fon the UK economy, Westminster echoed
OL,16,Fonce again to the sounds of civil war.
OL,18,FKeir Starmer has raised his standard.
OL,19,FWes Streeting has strapped on his
OL,20,Farmour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
